  20:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim.c ****   *           + TIM Input Capture Start Interruption
  21:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim.c ****   *           + TIM Input Capture Start DMA
  22:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim.c ****   *           + TIM One Pulse Initialization
