7861:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV1: ETRP Prescaler OFF.
7862:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV2: ETRP frequency divided by 2.
7863:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV4: ETRP frequency divided by 4.
7864:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV8: ETRP frequency divided by 8.
