7867:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPOLARITY_INVERTED: active low or falling edge active.
7868:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPOLARITY_NONINVERTED: active high or rising edge active.
7869:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim.c ****   * @param  ExtTRGFilter External Trigger Filter.
7870:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim.c ****   *          This parameter must be a value between 0x00 and 0x0F
7871:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_tim.c ****   * @retval None
